# Cream Corn Fritters

Makes 8

## Ingredients

* 400g creamed corn
* 1 egg
* 1 cup SR flour
* dash salt

## Extras

* mixed veg
* bacon
* cheese

## Method

1. Fry like a pancake

## Notes
